After giving plenty of hints about the sex of her baby on the way, Cardi B has confirmed that she is having a baby girl! The award-winning femcee was asked during the Howard Stern Show on SiriusXM’s by the host directly, “Do you know what you’re having … what are you having?” “Yes,” the rapper replied. “I’m having a girl.” <img class="wp-image-629309 size-medium lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this-880x598.jpg" alt="" width="880" height="598" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this-880x598.jpg 880w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this-487x331.jpg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this-974x662.jpg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this-320x218.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this-640x435.jpg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this-600x408.jpg 600w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/this.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px" /> The speculation about the sex of Cardi B and Offset’s baby by fans began when she co-hosted The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon the host gave her a gift basket with a purple blanket. At the just concluded Met Gala, the couple were together with Cardi B wearing Jeremy Scott as he walked along with her. At the event, Cardi B dropped yet another hint that her baby on the way is a little girl while catching up with the New York Times ahead of Met Gala, where she repeatedly referred to the baby as “she.” 25-year-old US hip-hop artiste, Cardi B first revealed she was pregnant with her first child by giving away her bump on stage while performing at the variety show Saturday Night Live. She sang her track Be Careful from her newly released debut album Invasion of Privacy while wearing a tight fitting white dress. At that time, sources hinted that the singer was over six months pregnant. Cardi B Photo credit: pinterest Offset one of the rappers from hip-hop trio Migos who is also her finance, tweeted after the reveal in capital letters: “Cardi and I look forward to our next chapter together.” Cardi B also tweeted: “I started winning when the whole world was doubting on me! Think imma lose with my little baby counting on me?” The couple became engaged in October. Cardi B and fiance Offset Photo credit: pinterest From stripper to proud mother Okurrr *in Cardi B’s voice*